    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p> <img style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/upload/onlineshop/2025-07-29/md-local-108-358.png\" alt=\"108GB本地365日數據卡\"></p>\n<p><span>108GB本地365日數據卡</span></p>\n\n<ul class=\"feature-list\">\n<li><span>一經啟用，即時扣除$358儲值額以開啟「啟用套裝」- 108GB本地數據用量+每30天贈送300分鐘本地通話(共送12次)</span></li>\n<li><span>增值後可選購多款本地及漫遊數據組合，價格低至$88有效期長達365日大中華數據組合</span></li>\n<li><span><span>無需登入，使用</span> <b><span><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/top-up\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>網站</span></strong></a> </span></b><span>隨時增值賬戶</span></span></li>\n<li><span><span>網上全自助服務：</span><b><span><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/my-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>登入網站</span></strong></a> </span></b><span>或透過</span> </span><b><a href=\"https://mylink.komect.com/mylink/?link=openpage://7501&umkey=mkt_prepaid#/l/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>MyLink App</span></strong></a></b> <span>輕鬆管埋賬戶及申請服務</span><span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"fee-section\">\n<div class=\"section-divider\"></div>\n<div>\n<hr>\n<p><span><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>啟用套裝</strong></span></p>\n\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<thead><tr>\n<th><span><strong>面值</strong></span></th>\n<th><span><strong>服務</strong></span></th>\n<th><span><strong>儲值額</strong></span></th>\n<th><span><strong>有效期<span><sup>#</sup></span></strong> </span></th>\n</tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span>$358</span></td>\n<td>\n<p><span>108GB本地數據用量+</span></p>\n<p><span>每30天贈送300分鐘本地通話</span><br><span>(共送12次)*</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>$0</span></p>\n<p><span>(此卡一經啟用，$358儲值額將隨即被扣除)</span></p>\n</td>\n<td><span>365日</span></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<div> </div>\n<div>\n<p><span><span><sup>#</sup></span>受制於智能卡套上所列之有效日期，此卡有效期為啟用翌日起計至第365日香港時間23:59。若組合有效期比儲值卡有效期長，當儲值卡有效期到期時，此卡所有服務將會自動暫停而不作另行通知。申請任何365日數據組合後儲值卡的有效期將會以原本儲值卡有效期或數據組合有效期兩者中的較後者為準。客戶需增值延長儲值卡有效期方可繼續使用服務。</span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p><span>*300分鐘本地通話為贈送服務，每30天贈送1次，每次有效期為30天。當每月本地通話用量累計達300分鐘後，將按用量收費HK$0.1/分鐘。贈送服務受數據流量服務所限。客人若取消啟用套裝數據組合，並重新申請其他數據組合，餘下的免費本地通話分鐘及未使用的贈送服務亦會一併被取消。當儲值卡啟用套裝的數據流量服務已用完，中國移動香港保留隨即終止餘下及數據用量以外之服務（包括但不限於通話分鐘及短訊）的權利，不論是否還有未使用的贈送服務内容，而恕不另行通知。如有任何爭議，中國移動香港保留最終決定權。</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<p><strong><span><span><b>全新升級及多款組合推出</b></span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span><span>立即登入</span><b><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/my-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>網站</span></strong></a></b><span>或</span><b><a href=\"https://mylink.komect.com/mylink/?link=openpage://7501&umkey=mkt_prepaid#/l/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>MyLink App</span></strong></a></b><span>申請 / 取消組合，或可透過</span><b><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/upload/onlineshop/2026-02-03/mobile-duck-2-ussd-tc.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>短碼</span></strong></a></b><span>辦理。</span></span></li>\n<li><span>數據用量達上限後，數據服務將會自動終止，客戶如需繼續使用數據服務，客戶需先取消原有組合，並重新申請其他數據組合，而原有數據組合中未用完之用量亦會被取消。</span></li>\n<li><span><span><span>如需使用漫遊服務，請按*109*01#打出電話或登入</span><b><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/my-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>網站</span></strong></a></b><span>或</span><b><a href=\"https://mylink.komect.com/mylink/?link=openpage://7501&umkey=mkt_prepaid#/l/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>MyLink App</span></strong></a></b><span>以啟動漫遊服務。</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><span></span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span>本地數據組合</span></strong></p>\n\n<div>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><strong>收費</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>本地服務組合</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>有效期</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$88</span></p>\n<p><span><b>（優惠價</b><b>$78</b><b>）</b></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>•30GB+任用<sup>^</sup></p>\n<p>•5,000本地通話</p>\n<p>•50個本地網内短信</p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>1GB</b><b>内地及澳門共享數據</b></span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<p><span><span>30日</span><sup><span>+</span><sup></sup></sup></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$118</span></p>\n<p><span><b>（優惠價</b><b>$108</b><b>）</b></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>•60GB+任用<sup>^</sup></p>\n<p>•5,000本地通話</p>\n<p>•50個本地網内短信</p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>2GB</b><b>内地及澳門共享數據</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$68</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•10GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"8\">\n<p><span>365日</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$98</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•20GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$138</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•50GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>數據</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$148</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•60GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>數據</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$188</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•90GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>數據</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$228</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•110GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>數據</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$238</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•140GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>數據</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$248</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•160GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>數據</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<p><span><strong>本地及中國内地共用數據組合</strong></span><strong></strong></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><strong>收費</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>中國內地及本地共用服務組合</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>有效期</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$148</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•10GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p><span>180日</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$248</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•20GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$358</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•30GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$548</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•60GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$108</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•5GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">\n<p><span>365 日</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$168</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•15GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$268</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•25GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$378</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•40GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$498</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•55GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通話</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n<p><br><strong></strong></p>\n<p><span><b>中國內地、澳門、台灣共享漫遊數據組合</b></span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><strong>收費</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>共享用量</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>有效期</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$88</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>5GB</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>90日</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$138</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>10GB</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<p><span>365日</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$238</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>20GB</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<p><span><b>中國內地、本地、澳門、台灣四地共享漫遊組合</b></span></p>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>收費</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>共享用量</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span><strong>有效期</strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$158</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>12GB</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>365日</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<p><span><span><sup>^</sup>4.5G全速組合達指定用量後，其後高達2Mbps。</span><span></span></span></p>\n<p><span> <span><sup>+</sup></span>如儲值卡餘額充足，數據組合將自動續期，否則該服務將自動終止，恕不另行通知。</span></p>\n</div>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span></span></p>\n<div>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<thead><tr>\n<th><strong>服務<strong></strong></strong></th>\n<th><strong>收費<strong></strong></strong></th>\n</tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span>本地通話費</span></td>\n<td><span>24小時劃一價:$0.1/ 分鐘</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>短訊服務</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr>\n<td><span>本地網內短訊</span></td>\n<td><span>每個 $0.3</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>本地跨網短訊</span></td>\n<td><span>每個 $0.7</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>國際短訊至中國內地</span></td>\n<td><span>每個 $1.5</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>國際短訊</span></td>\n<td><span>每個 $1.8</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>漫遊時發出短訊附加費</span></td>\n<td><span>每個 $3</span></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<br><br>\n\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>多媒體訊息服務（MMS)</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr>\n<td><span>發出多媒體訊息</span></td>\n<td><span>每個 $1</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>發出國際多媒體訊息附加費</span></td>\n<td><span>每個 $3</span></td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n<span>由2023年11月30日起，儲值卡之本地發出多媒體訊息收費將由每個$0.5調整至每個$1</span></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<p><span><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/upload/onlineshop/2026-02-03/mobile-duck-2-data-service-tnc-tc.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>按此</span></strong></a>了解服務條款及細則詳情。</span></p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p> <img style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/upload/onlineshop/2025-07-29/md-local-108-358.png\"></p>\n<p><span>108GB 365-day Local Data Prepaid SIM Card</span></p>\n\n<ul class=\"feature-list\">\n<li><span>Upon activation, $358 stored value will be deducted immediately for service activation for 365 days 108GB Local Data+every 30days free 300 minutes local(total 12 times)</span></li>\n<li><span>After refill, you can subscribe to multiple local and roaming data packages, price as low as $88 and validity up to 365 days of Greater China data package</span></li>\n<li><span>No login needed. Top up anytime via our</span> <b><span><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/en/home/top-up\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>Prepaid Refill</span></strong></a></span></b><span> <span>page</span></span></li>\n<li><span>Everything Online – Log in to</span> <a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/en/home/my-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>CMHK Website</span></strong></a> or <a href=\"https://mylink.komect.com/mylink/?link=openpage://7501&umkey=mkt_prepaid#/l/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>MyLink App</span></strong></a> <span>to manage your account and subscribe to our services at your fingertips</span> </li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n</div>\n<div class=\"fee-section\">\n<div class=\"section-divider\"></div>\n<div>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h3 class=\"fee-title\"><strong><h3 class=\"fee-title\">Starter Pack</h3></strong></h3>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<thead><tr>\n<th><strong><span>Face Value</span></strong></th>\n<th><strong><span>Services</span></strong></th>\n<th><strong><span>Stored Value</span></strong></th>\n<th><strong><span>Validity Period<sup>#</sup></span></strong></th>\n</tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span>$358</span></td>\n<td>\n<p><span>108GB Local Data Usage+</span></p>\n<p><span>Free 300 minutes local airtime every 30 days</span><br><span>(total of 12 times)*</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>$0</span></p>\n<p><span>($358 stored value will be deducted upon SIM activation)</span></p>\n</td>\n<td><span>365 days</span></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<div>\n<div> </div>\n<div>\n<p><span><span><sup>#</sup></span>Subject to the expiry date as printed on the SIM Cardholder, mobile data service is valid from the next day upon activation to the 365th day 23:59 (Hong Kong time). If the package validity period is longer than the prepaid SIM card validity period, the service will be suspended without prior notice when the SIM card validity expires. After subscribing to any 365 days data package, the validity of your Prepaid SIM Card will subject to either the original SIM validity or validity of the data package, to which has a longer period. Customers are required to refill the SIM card to extend the validity in order to re-activate the service.</span></p>\n<p><span>*The 300 minutes of local airtime are provided as a complimentary service, given once every 30 days, with a validity period of 30 days per allocation. Once the monthly usage of local airtime reaches 300 minutes, additional usage will be charged at HK$0.1 per minute. The entitlement to complimentary services is contingent upon the mobile data included in the starter package. Cancellation of the starter pack and subscription of any new data package will reset the free local airtime immediately, the unused complimentary services will also be canceled. If the mobile data is fully consumed, CMHK reserves the right to terminate any remaining package entitlement and non-data services (including but not limited to voice calls and SMS usage) immediately, regardless of whether there are unused complimentary services remaining. CMHK retains the right to make the final decision in the event of any disputes.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p><span><b>Several new and optimized data </b><b>packages</b><b> have been launched</b></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span><span><span>Log in to</span> <a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/en/home/my-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>CMHK Website</span></strong></a> <span>or</span> <a href=\"https://mylink.komect.com/mylink/?link=openpage://7501&umkey=mkt_prepaid#/l/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>MyLink App</span></strong></a> <span>MyLink </span><span><span>for data package subscription & management, or subscribe via</span> <a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/upload/onlineshop/2026-02-03/mobile-duck-2-ussd-en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>USSD Code</span></strong></a><span>.</span></span></span></span></li>\n<li><span>When the cumulated data usage for the package reaches the upper limit during the validity period, data service will be suspended. If further data service is needed, customers are required to re-subscription after cancelling the service, any unused usage in the existing data package will be forfeited.</span></li>\n<li><span>To use the roaming service, please press *109*01# to activate.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span><strong><span></span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span><strong><span>Local Data Package</span></strong></span></p>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><strong><span>Charge</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<h3 class=\"fee-title\"><strong><span>Local Service Package</span></strong></h3>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong><span>Validity</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$88</span></p>\n<p><span><strong><span>（Special Price $78）</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•30GB+Unlimited Local Data<sup>^</sup></span></p>\n<p><span>•5,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n<p><span>•50 Local Intra SMS</span></p>\n<p><span><b>Free 1GB Chinese Mainland & Macau, China roaming data</b></span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<p><span>30 days<sup>+</sup></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$118</span></p>\n<p><span>（Special Price $108）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•60GB+Unlimited Local Data<sup>^</sup></span></p>\n<p><span>•5,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n<p><span><b>•</b>50 Local Intra SMS</span></p>\n<p><span><b>Free 2GB Chinese Mainland & Macau, China roaming data</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$68</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•10GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"8\">\n<p><span>365 days</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$98</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•20GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$138</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•50GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n<p><span><b>Free 3GB Chinese Mainland roaming data</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$148</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•60GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n<p><span><b>Free 3GB Chinese Mainland roaming data</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$188</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•90GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n<p><span><b>Free 3GB Chinese Mainland roaming data</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$228</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•110GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n<p><span><b>Free 3GB Chinese Mainland roaming data</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$238</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•140GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n<p><span><b>Free 3GB Chinese Mainland roaming data</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$248</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•160GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n<p><span><b>Free 3GB Chinese Mainland roaming data</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<p><span><b>Local & Chinese Mainland Shared Data Package</b></span></p>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><strong><span>Charge</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<h3 class=\"fee-title\"><strong><span>Chinese Mainland & Local Data Package</span></strong></h3>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong><span>Validity</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$148</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•10GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"4\">\n<p><span>180 days</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$248</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•20GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$358</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•30GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$548</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•60GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$108</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•5GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"5\">\n<p><span>365 days</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$168</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•15GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$268</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•25GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•1,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$378</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•40GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$498</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•55GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000 mins local voice</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<p><span><b>Chinese Mainland & Macau & Taiwan Shared Roaming Data Package</b></span></p>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><strong><span>Charge</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong><span>Shared Roaming Data Usage</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong><span>Validity</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$88</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>5GB</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>90 days</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$138</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>10GB</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<p><span>365 days</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$238</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>20GB</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<p><span><b>Chinese Mainland & Local & Macau & Taiwan Shared Data</b></span></p>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><strong>Charge</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>Shared Roaming Data Usage</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>Validity</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$158</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>12GB</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>365 days</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<p><span><sup>^</sup>4.5G full speed package reaches the specified usage, thereafter up to 2Mbps.</span></p>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p><span><sup>+</sup>If the balance with sufficient stored value, data package will be auto-renewed, otherwise, the service will be automatically terminated without further notice.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<thead><tr>\n<th><strong>Service</strong></th>\n<th><strong>Charges</strong></th>\n</tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span>Local Airtime Charge</span></td>\n<td><span>24-hr Flat Rate: $0.1/min</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>Short Message Service</span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div><span> </span>\n\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr>\n<td><span>Local Intra-network SMS</span></td>\n<td><span>$0.3/SMS</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>Local Inter-network SMS</span></td>\n<td><span>$0.7/SMS</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>International SMS to Mainland China</span></td>\n<td><span>$1.5/SMS</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>International SMS</span></td>\n<td><span>$1.8/SMS</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>Surcharge on sending International SMS</span></td>\n<td><span>$3/SMS</span></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>Multimedia Messaging Service (MMS)<sup>11</sup></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<div><span> </span>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr>\n<td><span>Send MMS</span></td>\n<td><span>$1/MMS</span></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><span>Surcharge on sending International MMS</span></td>\n<td><span>$3/MMS</span></td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<p><span>Effective from 30 November 2023, the charge of local send MMS will be adjusted from $0.5 to $1</span></p>\n</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<p><span>Please <a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/upload/onlineshop/2026-02-03/mobile-duck-2-data-service-tnc-en.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>click here</span></strong></a> for more information on any services.</span></p>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p> <img style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\" src=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/upload/onlineshop/2025-07-29/md-local-108-358.png\" alt=\"108GB本地365日数据卡\"></p>\n<p><span>108GB本地365日数据卡</span></p>\n\n<ul class=\"feature-list\">\n<li><span>一经啟用，即时扣除$358儲值額以开啟「啟用套裝」- 108GB本地数据用量+每30天贈送300分鐘本地通话(共送12次)</span></li>\n<li><span>充值后可选购多款本地及漫遊数据组合，价格低至$88有效期长达365日大中华数据组合</span></li>\n<li><span><span>無需登入，使用</span> <b><span><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/top-up\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>网站</span></strong></a> </span></b><span>随时充值賬戶</span></span></li>\n<li><span><span>网上全自助服务：</span><b><span><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/my-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>登入网站</span></strong></a> </span></b><span>或透过</span> </span><b><a href=\"https://mylink.komect.com/mylink/?link=openpage://7501&umkey=mkt_prepaid#/l/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>MyLink App</span></strong></a></b> <span>輕鬆管埋賬戶及申请服务</span><span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n</div>\n<div class=\"fee-section\">\n<div class=\"section-divider\"></div>\n<div>\n<hr>\n<p><span><strong></strong></span></p>\n<p><span><strong>啟用套裝</strong></span></p>\n\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<thead><tr>\n<th><span><strong>面值</strong></span></th>\n<th><span><strong>服务</strong></span></th>\n<th><span><strong>儲值額</strong></span></th>\n<th><span><strong>有效期<span><sup>#</sup></span></strong> </span></th>\n</tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><span>$358</span></td>\n<td>\n<p><span>108GB本地数据用量+</span></p>\n<p><span>每30天贈送300分鐘本地通话</span><br><span>(共送12次)*</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>$0</span></p>\n<p><span>(此卡一经啟用，$358儲值額將随即被扣除)</span></p>\n</td>\n<td><span>365日</span></td>\n</tr>\n\n</tbody></table>\n<div> </div>\n<div>\n<p><span><span><sup>#</sup></span>受制於智能卡套上所列之有效日期，此卡有效期为啟用翌日起计至第365日香港时间23:59。若组合有效期比儲值卡有效期长，當儲值卡有效期到期时，此卡所有服务將会自动暫停而不作另行通知。申请任何365日数据组合后儲值卡的有效期將会以原本儲值卡有效期或数据组合有效期兩者中的較后者为準。客戶需充值延长儲值卡有效期方可繼续使用服务。</span></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<p><span>*300分鐘本地通话为贈送服务，每30天贈送1次，每次有效期为30天。當每月本地通话用量累计达300分鐘后，將按用量收費HK$0.1/分鐘。贈送服务受数据流量服务所限。客人若取消啟用套裝数据组合，並重新申请其他数据组合，餘下的免費本地通话分鐘及未使用的贈送服务亦会一併被取消。當儲值卡啟用套裝的数据流量服务已用完，中国移动香港保留随即終止餘下及数据用量以外之服务（包括但不限於通话分鐘及短信）的權利，不论是否还有未使用的贈送服务内容，而恕不另行通知。如有任何爭議，中国移动香港保留最終決定權。</span></p>\n</div>\n\n<p><strong><span><span><b>全新升级及多款组合推出</b></span></span></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span><span>立即登入</span><b><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/my-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>网站</span></strong></a></b><span>或</span><b><a href=\"https://mylink.komect.com/mylink/?link=openpage://7501&umkey=mkt_prepaid#/l/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>MyLink App</span></strong></a></b><span>申请 / 取消组合，或可透过</span><b><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/upload/onlineshop/2026-02-03/mobile-duck-2-ussd-tc.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>短碼</span></strong></a></b><span>辦理。</span></span></li>\n<li><span>数据用量达上限后，数据服务將会自动終止，客戶如需繼续使用数据服务，客戶需先取消原有组合，並重新申请其他数据组合，而原有数据组合中未用完之用量亦会被取消。</span></li>\n<li><span><span><span>如需使用漫遊服务，请按*109*01#打出电话或登入</span><b><a href=\"https://www.hk.chinamobile.com/tc/home/my-zone\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>网站</span></strong></a></b><span>或</span><b><a href=\"https://mylink.komect.com/mylink/?link=openpage://7501&umkey=mkt_prepaid#/l/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><strong><span>MyLink App</span></strong></a></b><span>以啟动漫遊服务。</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong><span></span></strong></p>\n<p><strong><span>本地数据组合</span></strong></p>\n\n<div>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\n<tr tr=\"\">\n<td>\n<p><strong>收費</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>本地服务组合</strong></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><strong>有效期</strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$88</span></p>\n<p><span><b>（优惠价</b><b>$78</b><b>）</b></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>•30GB+任用<sup>^</sup></p>\n<p>•5,000本地通话</p>\n<p>•50個本地网内短信</p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>1GB</b><b>内地及澳门共享数据</b></span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"2\">\n<p><span><span>30日</span><sup><span>+</span><sup></sup></sup></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$118</span></p>\n<p><span><b>（优惠价</b><b>$108</b><b>）</b></span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p>•60GB+任用<sup>^</sup></p>\n<p>•5,000本地通话</p>\n<p>•50個本地网内短信</p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>2GB</b><b>内地及澳门共享数据</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$68</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•10GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通话</span></p>\n</td>\n<td rowspan=\"8\">\n<p><span>365日</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$98</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•20GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通话</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$138</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•50GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通话</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>数据</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$148</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•60GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通话</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>数据</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$188</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•90GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通话</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>数据</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$228</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•110GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通话</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>数据</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$238</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•140GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通话</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>数据</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n<p><span>$248</span></p>\n</td>\n<td>\n<p><span>•160GB</span></p>\n<p><span>•2,000本地通话</span></p>\n<p><span><b>送</b><b>3GB</b><b>内地</b><b>漫遊</b><b>数据</b></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n<p><span><strong>本地及中国内地共用数据组合</strong></span><strong></strong></p>\n</div>\n<div>\n<table class=\"fee-table\">\n\