    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20230509/P0000429%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%803%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2%E5%8D%A1$48(Daily%203GB%20FUP).png\" alt=\"澳門上網卡 1日 HK$18\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 東盟 -->\n  <div class=\"tt-title\">\n    基本信息\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">數據用量</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">每日3GB高速數據，當澳門數據用量達到每日3GB「公平使用數據用量上限」(至翌日香港時間00:00開始重新計算)，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將被減慢及限制(但不低於256kbps)，並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸 。\n    </span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日數</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">3日。SIM卡啟用後起計，至第3日香港時間23:59結束。</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">有效期</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">覆蓋地區</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">澳門</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">可否增值</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值。</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">啟用地點</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">澳門</span>\n  </div>\n  <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">即買即用</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">\n      實體SIM卡插入電話後即可自動啟用；eSIM掃描激活二維碼後即可自動啟用。使用有效期亦已開始計算。\n\n      《電訊（登記用戶識別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效，根據該《規例》，\n      自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的預付儲值卡必須先完成實名登記才啓用有關電訊服務。\n    </span>\n  </div> -->\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM類型</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal&nbsp;SIM&nbsp;三合一&nbsp;(適合各款手機)</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">使用指南</span>\n    <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n        target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20230509/P0000429%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%803%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2%E5%8D%A1$48(Daily%203GB%20FUP).png\" alt=\"澳門上網卡 1日 HK$18\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 東盟 -->\n  <div class=\"tt-title\">\n    Basic Information\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Useuse of data</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">It provides 4G network unlimited data usage in Macau\n      (Once your daily data usage in Macau reaches “Fair Usage level”\n      3GB(calculation of data usage will be re-started from HK time 00:00 next day), the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted\n      (but not below 256kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.\n    </span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Data validity period</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">3-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 3rd day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Validity period</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Coverage area</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Macau</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Whether add value</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Enable the location</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Macau</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM type</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Nano, Micro, Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">User Guide</span>\n    <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n        target=\"_blank\">Click here to view </a></span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20230509/P0000429%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%803%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%8A%E7%B6%B2%E5%8D%A1$48(Daily%203GB%20FUP).png\" alt=\"澳门上网卡 1日 HK$18\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 东盟 -->\n  <div class=\"tt-title\">\n    基本信息\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">数据用量</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">每日3GB高速数据，當澳门数据用量达到每日3GB「公平使用流量用量上限」(至翌日香港时间00:00开始重新计算)，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制(但不低於256kbps)，並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。\n    </span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日数</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">3日。SIM卡啟用后起计，至第3日香港时间23:59结束。</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">有效期</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">覆蓋地区</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">澳门</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">可否充值</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">啟用地点</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">澳门</span>\n  </div>\n  <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">即买即用</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">\n      实体SIM卡插入电话后即可自动啟用；eSIM掃描激活二维碼后即可自动啟用。使用有效期亦已开始计算。\n\n      《电讯（登记用戶识別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效，根据该《規例》，\n      自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的预付儲值卡必須先完成实名登记才啓用有关电讯服务。\n    </span>\n  </div> -->\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM類型</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal&nbsp;SIM&nbsp;三合一&nbsp;(適合各款手机)</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">使用指南</span>\n    <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n        target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span