    "summaryCn": "香港、澳门 | 4日 | 2GB",
    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250818/hkmc4-chi.jpg\" alt=\"香港及澳門多日上網卡 4日 2GB HK$25\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n        基本信息\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">實名登記</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">《電訊（登記用戶識別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效。根據該《規例》， 自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的預付儲值卡必須先完成實名登記才可啓用有關電訊服務。將實體SIM卡插入手機或將eSIM下載安裝至手機以完成實名登記後即可啟用服務。<a href=\"https://www.cuniq.com/global/HKRealNameRegistration\" target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >按此登記</a\r\n        ></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">數據用量</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">每日2GB高速數據，當香港及澳門共用數據用量達到每日2GB「公平使用數據用量上限」(至翌日中國香港時間00:00開始重新計算)，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將被減慢及被控於512kbps，並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">可用日數</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">4日。啟用儲值卡當日起計之第4日(香港時間) 23:59終止。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">覆蓋地區</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">香港、澳門</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">話音/短訊</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">可否增值</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">啟用地點</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">香港、澳門</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM類型</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">使用指南</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n\t     <span style=\"width: 110px\">eSIM</span>\r\n\t     <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n\t </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250818/hkmc4-chi.jpg\" alt=\"香港及澳門多日上網卡 4日 2GB HK$25\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">Basic information</div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Real-Name Registration</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Once inserted into the mobile device, the SIM will be activated; For eSIM, scan the activation QR code. The validity period of the SIM card service starts from the day it is activated and the service is commenced. The Telecommunications (Registration of SIM Cards) Regulation (“Regulation”) came into effect on 1st September 2021. Pursuant to the Regulation, prepaid SIM cards that can be used in Hong Kong must complete registration in order to activate or continue the use of telecommunications service from 1 March 2022. <a href=\"https://www.cuniq.com/global/HKRealNameRegistration\">Register Here</a>. </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">\r\n        It provides 5G/4G network unlimited data usage in Hong Kong and Macau (Once your daily data usage in Hong Kong and Macau  reaches “Fair Usage Level (FUP)” 2GB(calculation of data usage will be re-started from HK time 00:00 next day), the upload/download speed would be reduced and controlled at 512kbps and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.\r\n      </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">4-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 4th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Hong Kong, Macau</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n     <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Hong Kong, Macau</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">\r\n        <a\r\n          href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\r\n          target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >Click to view</a\r\n        >\r\n      </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\"\r\n        ><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >Click to view</a\r\n        ></span\r\n      >\r\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250818/hkmc4-chi.jpg\" alt=\"香港及澳门多日上网卡 4日 2GB HK$25\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n        基本信息\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">实名登记</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">《电讯（登记用戶识別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效。根据该《規例》， 自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的预付儲值卡必須先完成实名登记才可啓用有关电讯服务。將实体SIM卡插入手机或將eSIM下載安裝至手机以完成实名登记后即可啟用服务。<a href=\"https://www.cuniq.com/global/HKRealNameRegistration\" target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >按此登记</a\r\n        ></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">数据用量</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">每日2GB高速数据，當香港及澳门共用数据用量达到每日2GB「公平使用流量用量上限」(至翌日中国香港时间00:00开始重新计算)，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及被控於512kbps，並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">可用日数</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">4日。啟用儲值卡當日起计之第4日(香港时间) 23:59終止。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">覆蓋地区</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">香港、澳门</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">语音/短信</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">可否充值</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">啟用地点</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">香港、澳门</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM類型</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">使用指南</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n\t     <span style=\"width: 110px\">eSIM</span>\r\n\t     <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n\t </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
