    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250722/tc/P0000944.png\" alt=\"日本多日通話/上網卡 8GB HK$64\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n\t\tBasic Information\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data </span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 8GB mobile data service,  5G/4G network. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 8GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(controlled at 256kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.Requires a mobile phone equipped with VoLTE function.</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Data validity period </span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">5-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 5th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\n\t</div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Real-Name Registration</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">No need</span>\n\t</div> -->\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">Japan</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS storage value </span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">Japan</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">SIM type </span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">Click to\n\t\t\t\tview</a></span>\n\t</div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</ a></span>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250722/tc/P0000944.png\" alt=\"日本多日通话上网卡 8GB HK$64\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 日本-->\n    <div class=\"tt-title\">\n        基本信息\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">数据用量</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供8GB高速数据, 5G/4G网絡移动数据服务。 當於数据用量达到8GB「公平使用流量用量上限」，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（受控於256kbps），並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。需配備VoLTE功能的手机使用。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日数</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">5日。SIM卡啟用后起计，至第5日香港时间23:59结束。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">有效期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">覆蓋地区</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">日本</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">语音/短信</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">语音/短信儲值額</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">可否充值</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">啟用地点</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">日本</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM類型</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal&nbsp;SIM&nbsp;三合一&nbsp;(適合各款手机)</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">使用指南</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n                target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t<span style=\"width: 110px\">eSIM</span>\n\t\t<span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</ a></span>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
