    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/detail/mobile/20220220/southkorea5.jpg\" alt=\"南韓多日通話/上網卡 3日 HK$27\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 東南亞-->\n    <div class=\"tt-title\">\n        Basic Information\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">Fair use of data</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 4G network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage level\" 10GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 256kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">Data validity period</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">5-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 5th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">Validity period</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\n      </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">Coverage area</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">\n            South Korea</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">Voice/SMS</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card also provide 20 minutes voice call service in South Korea(to receive and make\n            outgoing calls to local, Mainland and Hong Kong number) and 10 SMS service credits (for sending SMS in South\n            Korea).</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">Whether add value</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\