    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/detail/mobile/20220220/southkorea5.jpg\" alt=\"韩国多日通话上网卡 5日/8日 HK$40\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 韩国-->\n    <div class=\"tt-title\">\n        基本信息\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">数据用量</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G网絡移动数据服务。 當於数据用量达到10GB「公平使用流量用量上限」，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於256kbps），並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日数</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">5日。SIM卡啟用后起计，至第5日香港时间23:59结束。</span>\n  </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">有效期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">覆蓋地区</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">韩国</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">语音/短信</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡並提供20分鐘通话(可用於韩国接听、致电當地、内地及香港号碼)及10 条短信（由韩国发送）。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">可否充值</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">啟用地点</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">韩国</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM類型</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal&nbsp;SIM&nbsp;三合一&nbsp;(適合各款手机)</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">使用指南</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n                target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">eSIM</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
