    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250610/2.png\" alt=\"越南多日通話/上網卡 2日 HK$18\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n    Basic Information\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Use of data</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">It provides 5G/4G network unlimited data usage in Vietnam (Once your daily data usage in Vietnam reaches “Fair Usage Level (FUP)” 2GB(calculation of data usage will be re-started from HK time 00:00 next day), the upload/download speed would be reduced and controlled at  512kbps and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Data validity period </span>\n    <span class=\"value\">2-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 2th day at 23:59 Hong Kong(China) time since card activation. </span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Validity period</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Coverage area</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Vietnam</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Whether add value</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Enable the location</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Vietnam</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">SIM type</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Use guide</span>\n    <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"/pc-static/prepaid-cards/Prepaid_card_user_guide_EN.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Click to\n        view</a></span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">eSIM</span>\n    <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"/pc-static/esim/compare-pc-chi1.png\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</a></span>\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250610/2.png\" alt=\"越南多日通话上网卡 2日 HK$18\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n            基本信息\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n            <span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span>\n            <span class=\"value\">每日2GB高速数据，當越南数据用量达到每日2GB「公平使用流量用量上限」(至翌日中国香港时间00:00开始重新计算)，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及受控於512kbps)，並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日数</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">2日。啟用儲值卡當日起计之第2日(中国香港时间) 23:59終止。</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n            <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\n            <span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n            <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span>\n            <span class=\"value\">越南</span>  </div>  \n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n            <span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span>\n            <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n            <span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span>\n            <span class=\"value\">越南</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n            <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\n            <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n            <span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span>\n            <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"detail--item\">\n            <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\n            <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n        </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
