    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20251023/thai5-chi.jpg\" alt=\"泰國多日上網卡 15日/30日/5日/7日/8日 5GB HK$25\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 泰國-->\n  <div class=\"tt-title\">\n    Basic Information\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Fair use of data</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 5GB mobile data service, 4G & LTE network in Thailand. Once your data usage reaches \"Fair usage level\" 5GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and controlled at 512kbps, and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Data validity period</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">5-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 5th day at 23:59 Hong Kong(China) time since card activation. </span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Validity period</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Coverage area </span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Thailand</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Voice/SMS</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Whether add value</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Enable the location </span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Thailand</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">SIM type</span>\n    <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\n  