    "summary": "馬來西亞、新加坡、泰國、印尼 | 15日 | 3GB",
    "summaryEn": "馬來西亞、新加坡、泰國、印尼 | 15日 | 3GB",
    "summaryCn": "马来西亚、新加坡、泰国、印尼 | 15日 | 3GB",
    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260527/malaysia5-chi.jpg\" alt=\"星馬泰及印尼多日通話/上網卡 15日 HK$76\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span><span class=\"value\">每日3GB高速數據，當新加坡、馬來西亞、泰國及印尼數據用量達到每日3GB「公平使用數據用量上限」(至翌日中國香港時間00:00開始重新計算)，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將被減慢及限制(但不低於512kbps)，並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸 。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可用日數</span><span class=\"value\">5日。啟用儲值卡當日起計之第5日(中國香港時間) 23:59終止。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">有效期</span><span class=\"value\">自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span><span class=\"value\">馬來西亞、新加坡、泰國、印尼</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">話音/短訊</span><span class=\"value\">此卡並提供20分鐘通話(可用於新加坡、馬來西亞、泰國、及印尼接聽、致電當地及中國香港號碼)及10 條短訊（由新加坡、馬來西亞、泰國、及印尼發送）。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可否增值</span><span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span><span class=\"value\">馬來西亞、新加坡、泰國、印尼</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span><span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260527/malaysia5-chi.jpg\" alt=\"星馬泰及印尼多日通話/上網卡 15日 HK$76\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">Basic Information</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data</span><span class=\"value\">It provides 5G/4G network unlimited data usage in Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand and Indonesia (Once your daily data usage in Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand and Indonesia  reaches “Fair Usage Level (FUP)” 3GB(calculation of data usage will be re-started from HK time 00:00 next day), the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted \n(but not below 512kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span><span class=\"value\">5-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 5th day at 23:59 Hong Kong(China) time since card activation. </span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span><span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span><span class=\"value\">Malaysia, Singapore, Thailand, Indonesia</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span><span class=\"value\">This SIM card also provide 20 minutes voice call service in Singapore, Malaysia, Thailand & Indonesia (to receive and make outgoing calls to local and Chinese Mainland and Hong Kong number) and 10 SMS service credits (for sending SMS in Singapore, Malaysi</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span><span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span><span class=\"value\">Malaysia, Singapore, Thailand, Indonesia</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span><span class=\"value\">Nano, Micro, Normal All-in-one SIM</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260527/malaysia5-chi.jpg\" alt=\"新马泰及印尼多日通话上网卡 15日 HK$76\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span><span class=\"value\">每日3GB高速数据，當新加坡、马来西亚、泰国及印尼数据用量达到每日3GB「公平使用流量用量上限」(至翌日中国香港时间00:00开始重新计算)，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制(但不低於512kbps)，並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可用日数</span><span class=\"value\">5日。啟用儲值卡當日起计之第5日(中国香港时间) 23:59終止。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">有效期</span><span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span><span class=\"value\">马来西亚、新加坡、泰国、印尼</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">语音/短信</span><span class=\"value\">此卡並提供20分鐘通话(可用於新加坡、马来西亚、泰国、及印尼接听、致电當地及中国香港号碼)及10 条短信（由新加坡、马来西亚、泰国、及印尼发送）。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span><span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span><span class=\"value\">马来西亚、新加坡、泰国、印尼</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span><span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
