    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/detail/mobile/southeast1.png\" alt=\"東南亞8日上網卡 8日 5GB HK$56\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 東南亞-->\r\n  <div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n    Basic Information\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Fair use of data</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 4G network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage level\" 5GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 256kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Data validity period</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">8-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 8th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Validity period</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Coverage area</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">Macau, Singapore, Thailand, Malaysia, Laos, Indonesia, Philippines, Cambodia, Vietnam, Sri Lanka</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Voice/SMS</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Whether add value</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">Enable the location</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">Macau, Singapore, Thailand, Malaysia, Laos, Indonesia, Philippines, Cambodia, Vietnam, Sri Lanka</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM type</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">User Guide</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">Click to\r\n        view</a></span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 110px\">eSIM</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</a></span>\r\n  </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/detail/mobile/southeast1.png\" alt=\"东南亚8日上网卡 8日 5GB HK$56\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 东南亚-->\r\n    <div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n        基本信息\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">数据用量</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G网絡移动数据服务。 當於数据用量达到5GB「公平使用流量用量上限」，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於256kbps），並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日数</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">8日。SIM卡啟用后起计，至第8日香港时间23:59结束。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">有效期</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">覆蓋地区</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">澳门、新加坡、泰国、马来西亚、老挝、印尼、菲律宾、柬埔寨、越南、斯里蘭卡</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">语音/短信</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">可否充值</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">啟用地点</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">澳门、新加坡、泰国、马来西亚、老挝、印尼、菲律宾、柬埔寨、越南、斯里蘭卡</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">SIM類型</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal&nbsp;SIM&nbsp;三合一&nbsp;(適合各款手机)</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 110px\">使用指南</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n