    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20240429/asia8_2.png\" alt=\"亞洲多日上網卡 12日/30日/8日 5GB HK$73\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 亞洲 -->\r\n  <div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n    Basic information\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Fair use of data</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">Once your total data usage in applicable regions reach \"Fair Usage level\" 5GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(but not below 256kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available. If using Japan roaming, Requires a mobile phone equipped with VoLTE function.</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Data validity period</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">8-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 8th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Validity period</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Real-Name Registration</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">No need</span>\r\n  </div> -->\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Coverage area</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">Macau(China), Japan, South Korea, Singapore, Thailand, Malaysia, Laos, Indonesia, Philippines, Cambodia, Vietnam, Sri Lanka</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Voice/SMS</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n    <span style=\"width: 200px\">Voice/SMS storage value</span>\r\n    <span class=\"value\">Not applicable</span>\r\n  </div