    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260422/eu15-chi.jpg\" alt=\"歐洲多日上網卡 15日/30日/90日 8GB HK$123\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span><span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G網絡流動數據服務。 當於數據用量達到8GB「公平使用數據用量上限」，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於256kbps），並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸 。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可用日數</span><span class=\"value\">15日。啟用儲值卡當日起計之第15日(中國香港時間) 23:59終止。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">有效期</span><span class=\"value\">自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span><span class=\"value\">英國、奧地利、比利時、保加利亞、克羅地亞、塞浦路斯、捷克共和國、丹麥、愛沙尼亞、芬蘭、法國、法屬圭亞那、德國、直布羅陀、希臘、瓜德羅普島、匈牙利、冰島、愛爾蘭、意大利、拉脫維亞、列支敦士登、立陶宛、盧森堡、馬耳他、馬提尼克、馬約特島、荷蘭、挪威、波蘭、葡萄牙、留尼汪、羅馬尼亞、斯洛伐克、斯洛文尼亞、西班牙、瑞典、瑞士</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">話音/短訊</span><span class=\"value\">不適用</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可否增值</span><span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span><span class=\"value\">英國、奧地利、比利時、保加利亞、克羅地亞、塞浦路斯、捷克共和國、丹麥、愛沙尼亞、芬蘭、法國、法屬圭亞那、德國、直布羅陀、希臘、瓜德羅普島、匈牙利、冰島、愛爾蘭、意大利、拉脫維亞、列支敦士登、立陶宛、盧森堡、馬耳他、馬提尼克、馬約特島、荷蘭、挪威、波蘭、葡萄牙、留尼汪、羅馬尼亞、斯洛伐克、斯洛文尼亞、西班牙、瑞典、瑞士</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span><span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260422/eu15-chi.jpg\" alt=\"歐洲多日上網卡 15日/30日/90日 8GB HK$123\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">Basic Information</div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data</span><span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 4G\r\n      network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 8GB, the upload/download\r\n      speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 256kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be\r\n      available.</span></div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span><span class=\"value\">15-Day. The SIM card\r\n      will be expired on the 15th day at 23:59 Hong Kong(China) time since card activation. </span></div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span><span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for\r\n      1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span></div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span><span class=\"value\">UK, Austria, Belgium, Bulgaria,\r\n      Croatia, Cyprus, Czech Republic, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, France, French Guiana, Germany, Gibraltar, Greece,\r\n      Guadeloupe, Hungary, Iceland, Ireland, Italy, Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxemburg, Malta, Martinique,\r\n      Mayotte, Netherlands, Norway, Poland, Portugal, Reunion, Romania, Slovakia, Slovenia, Spain, Sweden,\r\n      Switzerland</span></div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span><span class=\"value\">N/A</span></div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span><span class=\"value\">This SIM card is\r\n      non-rechargeable</span></div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span><span class=\"value\">UK, Austria, Belgium, Bulgaria,\r\n      Croatia, Cyprus, Czech Republic, Denmark, Estonia, Finland, France, French Guiana, Germany, Gibraltar, Greece,\r\n      Guadeloupe, Hungary, Iceland, Ireland, Italy, Latvia, Liechtenstein, Lithuania, Luxemburg, Malta, Martinique,\r\n      Mayotte, Netherlands, Norway, Poland, Portugal, Reunion, Romania, Slovakia, Slovenia, Spain, Sweden,\r\n      Switzerland</span></div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span><span class=\"value\">Nano, Micro, Normal All-in-one\r\n      SIM</span></div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span><span class=\"value\"><a\r\n        href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a></span>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a\r\n        href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260422/eu15-chi.jpg\" alt=\"欧洲多日上网卡 15日/30日/90日 8GB HK$123\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span><span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G网絡移动数据服务。 當於数据用量达到8GB「公平使用流量用量上限」，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於256kbps），並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可用日数</span><span class=\"value\">15日。啟用儲值卡當日起计之第15日(中国香港时间) 23:59終止。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">有效期</span><span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span><span class=\"value\">英国、奧地利、比利时、保加利亚、克罗地亚、塞浦路斯、捷克共和国、丹麥、爱沙尼亚、芬蘭、法国、法屬圭亚那、德国、直布罗陀、希臘、瓜德罗普岛、匈牙利、冰岛、爱尔蘭、意大利、拉脫维亚、列支敦士登、立陶宛、盧森堡、马耳他、马提尼克、马约特岛、荷蘭、挪威、波蘭、葡萄牙、留尼汪、罗马尼亚、斯洛伐克、斯洛文尼亚、西班牙、瑞典、瑞士</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">语音/短信</span><span class=\"value\">不適用</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span><span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span><span class=\"value\">英国、奧地利、比利时、保加利亚、克罗地亚、塞浦路斯、捷克共和国、丹麥、爱沙尼亚、芬蘭、法国、法屬圭亚那、德国、直布罗陀、希臘、瓜德罗普岛、匈牙利、冰岛、爱尔蘭、意大利、拉脫维亚、列支敦士登、立陶宛、盧森堡、马耳他、马提尼克、马约特岛、荷蘭、挪威、波蘭、葡萄牙、留尼汪、罗马尼亚、斯洛伐克、斯洛文尼亚、西班牙、瑞典、瑞士</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span><span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
