    "id": 45,
    "name": "澳紐多日通話/上網卡 HK$123",
    "nameEn": "Australia & New Zealand 90-Day Data SIM(50GB) HK$123",
    "nameCn": "澳纽多日通话上网卡 HK$123",
    "summary": "澳洲、 紐西蘭 | 50GB",
    "summaryEn": "澳洲、 紐西蘭 | 50GB",
    "summaryCn": "澳洲、 纽西蘭 | 50GB",
    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260430/au-90-50GB-chi.jpg\" alt=\"澳紐多日通話/上網卡 HK$123\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span><span class=\"value\">此卡提供5G/4G網絡流動數據服務。 50GB高速數據。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可用日數</span><span class=\"value\">90日。啟用儲值卡當日起計之第90日(香港時間) 23:59終止。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">有效期</span><span class=\"value\">自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span><span class=\"value\">澳洲、 紐西蘭</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">話音/短訊</span><span class=\"value\">不適用</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可否增值</span><span class=\"value\">客戶可於數據使用完畢或有效期到期後30日內為SIM卡增值以重新啟用以下服務<br>\n增值金額: HK$450<br>\n數據組合: 50GB 澳洲及紐西蘭數據<br>\n有效期: 90 日 <br><br>\n\n備註:<br>\n(1)當90日有効期到期或數據使用完畢時，數據功能會被暫停，未用完之數據用量將會作廢。如用戶需要繼續使用服務，用戶必須於30日內增值，否則SIM卡失效。<br>\n(2)有效期屆滿後或數據使用完畢後30日內，增值HK$450 可重新啟用數據組合(有效期90日)。<br>\n(3)重新啟用的數據組合的用量會從重新啟用之日起重新計算，並不會與之前到期未使用完畢的用量疊加。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span><span class=\"value\">澳洲、 紐西蘭</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span><span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260430/au-90-50GB-chi.jpg\" alt=\"澳紐多日通話/上網卡 HK$123\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">Basic Information</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data</span><span class=\"value\">It provides 50GB 5G/4G network mobile data service.</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span><span class=\"value\">90-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 30th day at 23:59 Hong Kong(China) time since card activation. </span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span><span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span><span class=\"value\">Australia, New Zealand</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span><span class=\"value\">N/A</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span><span class=\"value\">Customer can recharge the SIM card for service resumption in 30 days after the data is used up or the validity period expires<br>\nRe-charge amount: HK$450<br>\nData package: 50GB Australia, New Zealand Data<br>\nValidity period: 90 Days <br><br>\n\nNote: <br>\n(1) Once the 90-day validity period expires or all data has been consumed, data service will be suspended. Unused data will be forfeited. To continue to use the service, customer has to recharge the SIM card within 30 days after the data is used up or the validity period expires. Otherwise, the SIM card will no longer be valid.<br>\n(2) Customer can recharge HK$450 to the SIM card so as to reactivate data package(90-day validity period) within 30 days after all data has been consumed or validity period expires.<br>\n(3) The usage of reactivated data package will be recalculated from the data of reactivation, and will not be accumulated with the expired unused usage.</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span><span class=\"value\">Australia, New Zealand</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span><span class=\"value\">Nano, Micro, Normal All-in-one SIM</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260430/au-90-50GB-chi.jpg\" alt=\"澳纽多日通话上网卡 HK$123\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span><span class=\"value\">此卡提供5G/4G网絡移动数据服务。 50GB高速数据。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可用日数</span><span class=\"value\">90日。啟用儲值卡當日起计之第90日(香港时间) 23:59終止。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">有效期</span><span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span><span class=\"value\">澳洲、 纽西蘭</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">语音/短信</span><span class=\"value\">不適用</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span><span class=\"value\">客戶可於数据使用完畢或有效期到期后30日内为SIM卡充值以重新啟用以下服务<br>\n充值金額: HK$450<br>\n数据组合: 50GB 澳洲及纽西蘭数据<br>\n有效期: 90 日 <br><br>\n\n備註:<br>\n(1)當90日有効期到期或数据使用完畢时，数据功能会被暫停，未用完之数据用量將会作廢。如用戶需要繼续使用服务，用戶必須於30日内充值，否則SIM卡失效。<br>\n(2)有效期屆滿后或数据使用完畢后30日内，充值HK$450 可重新啟用数据组合(有效期90日)。<br>\n(3)重新啟用的数据组合的用量会从重新啟用之日起重新计算，並不会与之前到期未使用完畢的用量疊加。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span><span class=\"value\">澳洲、 纽西蘭</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span><span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
