  {
    "id": 48,
    "name": "美加墨30日上網卡 30日 12GB HK$121",
    "nameEn": "USA, Canada & Mexico 30-Day Data SIM (12GB) 30日 12GB HK$121",
    "nameCn": "美加墨30日上网卡 30日 12GB HK$121",
    "summary": "美國、加拿大、墨西哥 | 30日 | 12GB",
    "summaryEn": "美國、加拿大、墨西哥 | 30日 | 12GB",
    "summaryCn": "美国、加拿大、墨西哥 | 30日 | 12GB",
    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20240910/mjm12.png\" alt=\"美加墨30日上網卡 30日 12GB HK$121\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n</head>\n\n\n    <div class=\"tt-title\">\n        基本信息\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G網絡流動數據服務。 當於數據用量達到12GB「公平使用數據用量上限」，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於512kbps），並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸 。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日數</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">30日，以啟用時間起計每24小時為1日， 不足1小時亦以1小時計算，並以香港時間計算。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">美國、加拿大、墨西哥 </span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">可否增值</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值。</span>\n    </div>\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">最後啓用日期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">請參考卡套上的日期</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">美國、加拿大、墨西哥。但請注意SIMS卡插入手機並收到網絡訊號, 即已自動激活SIM卡並啟用服務。SIM卡服務之有效期由激活及啟用服當日起計。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20240910/mjm12.png\" alt=\"美加墨30日上網卡 30日 12GB HK$121\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n        Basic Information\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Fair useuse of data</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 4G network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 12GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 512kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">30-Day. Every 24 hours from the activation time is counted as one day, and any less than one hour is also counted as one hour, and is calculated in Hong Kong time.</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Real-name Registration</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Not required</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">USA, Canada, Mexico</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n    </div>\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n\t\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Last activation date</span>\n\t\t\t<span class=\"value\">Please refer to the back of the packing</span>\n\t</div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">USA, Canada, Mexico. Insert the SIM card into the mobile phone and the mobile network signal will be detected. This means the SIM card has been activated automatically and the service has been commenced. The validity period of the SIM card service starts from the day of activation and service commencement.</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20240910/mjm12.png\" alt=\"美加墨30日上网卡 30日 12GB HK$121\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n</head>\n\n\n    <div class=\"tt-title\">\n        基本信息\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G网絡移动数据服务。 當於数据用量达到12GB「公平使用流量用量上限」，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於512kbps），並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日数</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">30日，以啟用时间起计每24小时为1日， 不足1小时亦以1小时计算，並以香港时间计算。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">美国、加拿大、墨西哥 </span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span>\n    </div>\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">最后啓用日期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">请參考卡套上的日期</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">美国、加拿大、墨西哥。但请注意SIMS卡插入手机並收到网絡讯号, 即已自动激活SIM卡並啟用服务。SIM卡服务之有效期由激活及啟用服當日起计。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span>\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
