    "summary": "阿聯酋 (包含阿布扎比、迪拜、沙迦、阿治曼、烏姆蓋萬、哈伊馬角和富查伊拉) | 30日 | 4GB",
    "summaryEn": "阿聯酋 (包含阿布扎比、迪拜、沙迦、阿治曼、烏姆蓋萬、哈伊馬角和富查伊拉) | 30日 | 4GB",
    "summaryCn": "阿联酋 (包含阿布扎比、迪拜、沙迦、阿治曼、烏姆蓋万、哈伊马角和富查伊拉) | 30日 | 4GB",
    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20231218/UAE-4GB-chi.png\" alt=\"阿聯酋30日上網卡 30日 4GB HK$63\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n        基本信息\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供5G/4G網絡流動數據服務。 當於數據用量達到4GB「公平使用數據用量上限」，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於512kbps），並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸 。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日數</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">30日。SIM卡啟用後起計，至第30日香港時間23:59結束。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"> 自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">阿聯酋 (包含阿布扎比、迪拜、沙迦、阿治曼、烏姆蓋萬、哈伊馬角和富查伊拉)</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">話音/短訊</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">話音/短訊儲值額</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">可否增值</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">阿聯酋</span>\n    </div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用方式</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">SIM卡插入電話後即可自動啟用，使用有效期亦已開始計算。</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">即買即用</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">\n               實體SIM卡插入電話後即可自動啟用；eSIM掃描激活二維碼後即可自動啟用。使用有效期亦已開始計算。\n            《電訊（登記用戶識別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效，根據該《規例》，\n\t\t\t自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的預付儲值卡必須先完成實名登記才啓用有關電訊服務。\n\t\t\t</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n        target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a>\n\t\t</span>\n    </div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n  <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\n  <!-- <span class=\"value\">不適用</span> -->\n  <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n   </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20231218/UAE-4GB-chi.png\" alt=\"阿聯酋30日上網卡 30日 4GB HK$63\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n        Basic Information\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Useuse of data</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 5G/4G network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage level\" 4GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 512kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available. </span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">30-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 30th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\n    </div>\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">United Arab Emirates (Abu Dhabi, Dubai, Sharjah, Ajman, Umm Al Quwain, Ras Al Khaimah and Fujairah.)</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS storage value</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">United Arab Emirates</span>\n    </div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Enable method</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Once inserted into the mobile device, the SIM will be activated.\n            The validity period of the SIM card service starts from the day it is activated and the service is commenced. </span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">Use</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">\n                <a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n        target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a>\n\t\t\t</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"> <a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n        target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a>\n\t\t</span>\n    </div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n  <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\n  <!-- <span class=\"value\">N/A</span> -->\n  <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</a></span>\n   </div>\n\n\ns\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20231218/UAE-4GB-chi.png\" alt=\"阿联酋30日上网卡 30日 4GB HK$63\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n        基本信息\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供5G/4G网絡移动数据服务。 當於数据用量达到4GB「公平使用流量用量上限」，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於512kbps），並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日数</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">30日。SIM卡啟用后起计，至第30日香港时间23:59结束。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"> 自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">阿联酋 (包含阿布扎比、迪拜、沙迦、阿治曼、烏姆蓋万、哈伊马角和富查伊拉)</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">语音/短信</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">语音/短信儲值額</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">阿联酋</span>\n    </div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用方式</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">SIM卡插入电话后即可自动啟用，使用有效期亦已开始计算。</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">即买即用</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">\n               实体SIM卡插入电话后即可自动啟用；eSIM掃描激活二维碼后即可自动啟用。使用有效期亦已开始计算。\n            《电讯（登记用戶识別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效，根据该《規例》，\n\t\t\t自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的预付儲值卡必須先完成实名登记才啓用有关电讯服务。\n\t\t\t</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\n        target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a>\n\t\t</span>\n    </div>\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\n  <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\n  <!-- <span class=\"value\">不適用</span> -->\n  <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n   </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
