    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20240422/3010.png\" alt=\"沙特阿拉伯、埃及及土耳其30日上網卡 30日 6GB HK$161\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n        Basic information\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Fair useuse of data</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 4G network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 6GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 512kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">30-Day. Every 24 hours from the activation time is counted as one day, and any less than one hour is also counted as one hour, and is calculated in Hong Kong time.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Real-name Registration</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Not required</span>\r\n    </div> -->\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Saudi Arabia, Egypt & Turkey</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n    </div> -->\r\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS storage value</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n    </div> -->\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"title_\">Last activation date</span>\r\n\t\t\t<span class=\"value\">Please refer to the back of the packing</span>\r\n\t</div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Saudi Arabia, Egypt & Turkey. Insert the SIM card into the mobile phone and the mobile network signal will be detected. This means the SIM card has been activated automatically and the service has been commenced. The validity period of the SIM card service starts from the day of activation and service commencement.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span>\r\n       <span class=\"value\">Insert the SIM card into the mobile phone and the mobile network signal will be detected.</span>\r\n\t\t</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t<!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n  <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\r\n  <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n  <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</a></span>\r\n   </div> -->\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20240422/3010.png\" alt=\"沙特阿拉伯、埃及及土耳其30日上网卡 30日 6GB HK$161\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\n        基本信息\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G网絡移动数据服务。 當於数据用量达到6GB「公平使用流量用量上限」，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於512kbps），並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n      <span style=\"width: 110px\">可用日数</span>\n      <span class=\"value\">30日，以啟用时间起计每24小时为1日， 不足1小时亦以1小时计算，並以香港时间计算。</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\"> 30日，以啟用时间起计每24小时为1日， 不足1小时亦以1小时计算，並以香港时间计算。</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">沙特阿拉伯、埃及及土耳其 </span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">语音/短信</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">语音/短信儲值額</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span>\n    </div>\n\t\t    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">最后啓用日期</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">请參考卡套上的日期</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">沙特阿拉伯、埃及及土耳其。但请注意SIMS卡插入手机並收到网絡讯号, 即已自动激活SIM卡並啟用服务。SIM卡服务之有效期由激活及啟用服當日起计。</span>\n    </div>\n    <!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">即买即用</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">\n               实体SIM卡插入电话后即可自动啟用；eSIM掃描激活二维碼后即可自动啟用。使用有效期亦已开始计算。\n            《电讯（登记用戶识別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效，根据该《規例》，\n\t\t\t自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的预付儲值卡必須先完成实名登记才啓用有关电讯服务。\n\t\t\t</span>\n    </div> -->\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\n        <span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span>\n        <span class=\"value\">实体SIM卡插入电话后即可自动啟用</span>\n    </div>\n\t<!-- <div class=\"detail--item\">\n  <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\n  <span class=\"value\">不適用</span>\n  <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\n   </div> -->\n</div>\n</div>",
