  {
    "id": 57,
    "name": "內地、香港及澳門365日上網卡 365日 45GB HK$211",
    "nameEn": "Chinese Mainland & Hong Kong & Macau 365-Day Data SIM (36GB+9GB)",
    "nameCn": "内地、香港及澳门365日上网卡 365日 45GB HK$211",
    "summary": "中國内地、香港、澳門 | 365日 | 45GB",
    "summaryEn": "中國内地、香港、澳門 | 365日 | 45GB",
    "summaryCn": "中国内地、香港、澳门 | 365日 | 45GB",
    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260420/HKMCChina-365-chi.jpg\" alt=\"內地、香港及澳門365日上網卡 365日 45GB HK$211\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n        基本信息\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">實名登記</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">《電訊（登記用戶識別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效。根據該《規例》， 自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的預付儲值卡必須先完成實名登記才可啓用有關電訊服務。將實體SIM卡插入手機或將eSIM下載安裝至手機以完成實名登記後即可啟用服務。<a href=\"https://www.cuniq.com/global/HKRealNameRegistration\" target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >按此登記</a\r\n        ></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G/5G網絡流動數據服務。45GB 內地、香港及澳門數據。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">可用日數</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">365日。啟用儲值卡當日起計之第365日(香港時間) 23:59終止。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">中國内地、香港、澳門</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">可否增值</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">\r\n            客戶可於數據使用完畢或有效期到期後30日內為SIM卡增值以重新啟用以下服務<br/>\r\n            增值金額: HK$250<br/>\r\n            數據組合: 36GB 內地、香港及澳門數據<br/>\r\n            有效期: 365 日 <br/>\r\n\r\n            備註:<br/>\r\n            (1)當365日有效期到期或數據使用完畢時，數據功能會被暫停，未用完之數據用量將會作廢。如用戶需要繼續使用服務，用戶必須於30日內增值，否則SIM卡失效。<br/>\r\n            (2)有效期屆滿後或數據使用完畢後30日內，增值HK$250 可重新啟用數據組合(有效期365日)。<br/>\r\n            (3)重新啟用的數據組合的用量會從重新啟用之日起重新計算，並不會與之前到期未使用完畢的用量疊加。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">中國内地、香港、澳門</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n\t     <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\r\n\t     <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</ a></span>\r\n\t </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260420/HKMCChina-365-chi.jpg\" alt=\"內地、香港及澳門365日上網卡 365日 45GB HK$211\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">Basic information</div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Real-Name Registration</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">The Telecommunications (Registration of SIM Cards) Regulation (“Regulation”) came into effect on 1st September 2021. Pursuant to the Regulation, prepaid SIM cards that can be used in Hong Kong must complete Real-Name Registration in order to activate or continue the use of telecommunications service from 1 March 2022. Insert the physical SIM card into your mobile phone or download and install the eSIM to your mobile phone to complete the Real-Name Registration and then activate the service. <a href=\"https://www.cuniq.com/global/HKRealNameRegistration\">Register Here</a>. </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">\r\n        It provides 4G/5G network mobile data service, 45GB in Chinese Mainland & Hong Kong & Macau.\r\n      </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">365-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 365th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation.  </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Chinese Mainland, Hong Kong, Macau</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Customer can recharge the SIM card for service resumption in 365 days after the data is used up or the validity period expires<br>\r\n\t\tRe-charge amount: HK$250<br>\r\n\t\tData package: 36GB Chinese Mainland & Hong Kong & Macau Data<br>\r\n\t\tValidity period: 365 Days <br>\r\n\r\n\t\tNote: <br>\r\n\t\t(1) Once the 365-day validity period expires or all data has been consumed, data service will be suspended. Unused data will be forfeited. To continue to use the service, customer has to recharge the SIM card within 30 days after the data is used up or the validity period expires. Otherwise, the SIM card will no longer be valid.<br>\r\n\t\t(2) Customer can recharge HK$250 to the SIM card so as to reactivate data package(365-day validity period) within 30 days after all data has been consumed or validity period expires.<br>\r\n\t\t(3) The usage of reactivated data package will be recalculated from the data of reactivation, and will not be accumulated with the expired unused usage.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Chinese Mainland, Hong Kong, Macau</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">\r\n        <a\r\n          href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\"\r\n          target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >Click to view</a\r\n        >\r\n      </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\"\r\n        ><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >Click to view</a\r\n        ></span\r\n      >\r\n    </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260420/HKMCChina-365-chi.jpg\" alt=\"内地、香港及澳门365日上网卡 365日 45GB HK$211\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n        基本信息\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">实名登记</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">《电讯（登记用戶识別卡）規例》（以下簡稱「《規例》」）已於2021年9月1日生效。根据该《規例》， 自2022年3月1日起，可於本地使用的预付儲值卡必須先完成实名登记才可啓用有关电讯服务。將实体SIM卡插入手机或將eSIM下載安裝至手机以完成实名登记后即可啟用服务。<a href=\"https://www.cuniq.com/global/HKRealNameRegistration\" target=\"_blank\"\r\n          >按此登记</a\r\n        ></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">此卡提供4G/5G网絡移动数据服务。45GB 内地、香港及澳门数据。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span class=\"title_\">可用日数</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">365日。啟用儲值卡當日起计之第365日(香港时间) 23:59終止。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">有效期</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">中国内地、香港、澳门</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">\r\n            客戶可於数据使用完畢或有效期到期后30日内为SIM卡充值以重新啟用以下服务<br/>\r\n            充值金額: HK$250<br/>\r\n            数据组合: 36GB 内地、香港及澳门数据<br/>\r\n            有效期: 365 日 <br/>\r\n\r\n            備註:<br/>\r\n            (1)當365日有效期到期或数据使用完畢时，数据功能会被暫停，未用完之数据用量將会作廢。如用戶需要繼续使用服务，用戶必須於30日内充值，否則SIM卡失效。<br/>\r\n            (2)有效期屆滿后或数据使用完畢后30日内，充值HK$250 可重新啟用数据组合(有效期365日)。<br/>\r\n            (3)重新啟用的数据组合的用量会从重新啟用之日起重新计算，並不会与之前到期未使用完畢的用量疊加。</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">中国内地、香港、澳门</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n\t     <span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span>\r\n\t     <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</ a></span>\r\n\t </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
