    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20250926/au90-chi.jpg\" alt=\"澳洲90日上網卡 (50GB) 90日 50GB HK$157\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<!-- 澳紐 -->\r\n    <div class=\"tt-title\">\r\n        Basic Information\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">Fair useuse of data</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">It provides 50GB 5G/4G network mobile data service.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">Data validity period</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">90-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 90th day at 23:59 Hong Kong time since card activation. </span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n      <span style=\"width: 200px\">Validity period</span>\r\n      <span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">Coverage area</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Australia</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">Voice/SMS</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">N/A</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">Voice/SMS storage value</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Not applicable</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">Whether add value</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">Enable the location</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Australia</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">SIM type</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、 Normal All-in-one SIM</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n        <span style=\"width: 200px\">User Guide</span>\r\n        <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</a></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n\t<div class=\"detail--item\">\r\n  <span style=\"width: 200px\">eSIM</span>\r\n  <span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click to view</a></span>\r\n   </div>\n</div>\n</div>",
