  {
    "id": 59,
    "name": "巴基斯坦、哈薩克及指定中東多地上網卡 30日 HK$538",
    "nameEn": "Pakistan, Kazakhstan, Middle East Asian 30-Day Data SIM $338(4GB FUP) 30日 HK$538",
    "nameCn": "巴基斯坦、哈萨克斯坦及指定中东多地上网卡 30日 HK$538",
    "summary": "30日 | 4GB",
    "summaryEn": "30日 | 4GB",
    "summaryCn": "30日 | 4GB",
    "description": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260226/middleasia-30-4GB-chi.jpg\" alt=\"巴基斯坦、哈薩克及指定中東多地上網卡 30日 HK$538\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">數據用量</span><span class=\"value\">此卡提供5G/4G網絡流動數據服務。 當於數據用量達到4GB「公平使用數據用量上限」，客戶仍可使用流動數據服務，但其數據傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於512kbps），並且不可用於網絡分享及點對點傳輸 。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可用日數</span><span class=\"value\">30日。啟用儲值卡當日起計之第30日(中國香港時間) 23:59終止。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">有效期</span><span class=\"value\">自購買日起計一年內可啟用，逾期無效。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地區</span><span class=\"value\">孟加拉、巴基斯坦、阿联酋、哈薩克、吉爾吉斯、塔吉克、烏茲別克、阿曼</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">話音/短訊</span><span class=\"value\">不適用</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可否增值</span><span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可增值。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">啟用地點</span><span class=\"value\">孟加拉、巴基斯坦、阿联酋、哈薩克、吉爾吉斯、塔吉克、烏茲別克、阿曼</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span><span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手機)</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionEn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260226/middleasia-30-4GB-chi.jpg\" alt=\"巴基斯坦、哈薩克及指定中東多地上網卡 30日 HK$538\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">Basic Information</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Fair use of data</span><span class=\"value\">The SIM card provides 5G/4G network mobile data service. Once your total data usage reach \"Fair Usage Level (FUP)\" 4GB, the upload/download speed would be reduced and restricted(minimum 512kbps) and tethering and Peer-to-Peer services would not be available.</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Data validity period</span><span class=\"value\">30-Day. The SIM card will be expired on the 30th day at 23:59 Hong Kong(China) time since card activation. </span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Validity period</span><span class=\"value\">The prepaid card is valid for 1 year from the date of purchase. It will be invaild after expiry.</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Coverage area</span><span class=\"value\">Bangladesh, Pakistan, UAE, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Tajikistan, Uzbekistan, Oman</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Voice/SMS</span><span class=\"value\">N/A</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Whether add value</span><span class=\"value\">This SIM card is non-rechargeable</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">Enable the location</span><span class=\"value\">Bangladesh, Pakistan, UAE, Kazakhstan, Kyrgyzstan, Tajikistan, Uzbekistan, Oman</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM type</span><span class=\"value\">Nano, Micro, Normal All-in-one SIM</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">User Guide</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/en/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">Click here to view</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
    "descriptionCn": "<div class=\"product-desc-html\">\n<div class=\"desc-section\">\n<p><img src=\"https://www.cuniq.com/pc-static/prepaid-cards/20260226/middleasia-30-4GB-chi.jpg\" alt=\"巴基斯坦、哈萨克斯坦及指定中东多地上网卡 30日 HK$538\" style=\"max-width:350px;width:100%;height:auto;\"></p>\n<div class=\"tt-title\">基本信息</div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">数据用量</span><span class=\"value\">此卡提供5G/4G网絡移动数据服务。 當於数据用量达到4GB「公平使用流量用量上限」，客戶仍可使用移动数据服务，但其数据傳輸速度將被減慢及限制（但不低於512kbps），並且不可用於网絡分享及点对点傳輸 。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可用日数</span><span class=\"value\">30日。啟用儲值卡當日起计之第30日(中国香港时间) 23:59終止。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">有效期</span><span class=\"value\">自购买日起计一年内可啟用，逾期無效。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">覆蓋地区</span><span class=\"value\">孟加拉、巴基斯坦、阿联酋、哈萨克斯坦、吉尔吉斯、塔吉克、烏茲別克、阿曼</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">语音/短信</span><span class=\"value\">不適用</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">可否充值</span><span class=\"value\">此SIM卡不可充值。</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">啟用地点</span><span class=\"value\">孟加拉、巴基斯坦、阿联酋、哈萨克斯坦、吉尔吉斯、塔吉克、烏茲別克、阿曼</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">SIM類型</span><span class=\"value\">Nano、Micro、Normal SIM 三合一 (適合各款手机)</span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">使用指南</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/services/travel-card-guide-n\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div><div class=\"detail--item\"><span class=\"title_\">eSIM</span><span class=\"value\"><a href=\"https://store.cuniq.com/tc/esim-module\" target=\"_blank\">按此查看</a></span></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
